Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,them are ones that I wanted to ask. So\Nthey'll be kind of a combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um why is it that we feel that life is\Nso difficult here on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, it's because it is\Nto begin with. You got to defy gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all day long.\N>> You were hitting the mic with your king.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N>> That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> To begin with, you have to defy defy\Ndefy gravity all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> You know, you're standing up vertically\Nlike this on on on a narrow platform
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,just two feet\Nand all kinds of things jostle you and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,push you. And then you have a certain\Nnumber of senses and they're also
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,assaulted.\Nvision. You got to watch all these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,things here and you got to listen to\Neverything that's going on. You have to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,be careful not to bump into things. And\Nhuman body, as tough as it may seem, is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,really quite fragile. I mean, you can\Nbreak it pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All you got to do is push it over a\Ncliff or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That'll do it.\N>> Push it into a lake and you're done with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it.\NYou know it it it takes constant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness. So no matter what we're doing\Nin the back of our mind there is always
