Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're being reported recorded\Ncorrectly and that the lighting will be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sufficient. So, I'm making a dozen\Npresumptions already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then this airplane keeps going right\Nover our head to try and drone out our
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,microphone.\NAnyway, all right. Yes. Survival is uh
