Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you're attributing it to the physical.\N>> Yes. Yes. Yeah. The psychological is a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,whole different program,\N>> but but just staying physically alive
