Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's being properly recorded and\Nthat we have a safe secure place to sit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that our safety is assured that our\Nsurvival is guaranteed. Mhm.
